model.name: Bliss Pump
model.disambiguatingDescription: The Bliss pump is an elegant style in velvety black suede baby goat leather. It is characterized by its feminine cut-away sides and low block heel, which is embellished with a gold-tone LV accessory inspired by the clasp of the iconic Dauphine bag. This model is finished with a leather outsole.
